msgstr "¿Cómo puedo obtener una versión de prueba beta de Python?"

#: ../../faq/general.rst:229
msgid ""
"Alpha and beta releases are available from https://www.python.org/"
"downloads/.  All releases are announced on the comp.lang.python and comp."
